                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Take What You Can Get!</h5>
                            <p>Take Advantage of Tax Credits: Tax credits can help reduce the amount of tax you owe. For example, the Earned Income Tax Credit (EITC) 
                                is a tax credit for low- to moderate-income workers. The credit is refundable, which means you could receive a refund even if you don't owe any taxes.
                            </p>                       
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center col-sm-6 mb-3 col-lg-3 mb-sm-0 my-4 option-card">
            <div class="card-wrapper">
                <div class="card" id="info">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Details, Details, Details...</h5>                      
                            <p>Itemize Your Deductions: Itemizing your deductions can help you lower your taxable income. Deductions include things like charitable contributions, mortgage 
                            interest, and state and local taxes.
                            </p>                       
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="text-center col-sm-6 mb-3 col-lg-3 mb-sm-0 my-4 option-card">
