                        <h5 class="card-title">Always Give Back</h5>
                            <p>
                                Donate to Charity: Donating to charity is not only a good way to give back, but it can also help lower your taxes. 
                                Charitable contributions are tax-deductible, so be sure to keep track of any donations you make throughout the year.
                            </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
