                        <h5 class="card-title">Why Not?</h5>                        
                            <p>Maximize Your Tax Deductions: Maximize your tax deductions by keeping track of all eligible expenses. 
                                For example, if you're self-employed, you may be able to deduct expenses like home office expenses, mileage, and equipment costs.
                            </p>                        
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
