                                Take Advantage of Tax Loss Harvesting: If you have investments that have lost value, you can sell those investments to offset any gains 
                                you may have and lower your tax liability. It's important to note that tax laws can change, and it's always best to consult with a tax 
                                professional before making any decisions that could impact your taxes.
                                </p>                        
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
